					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-97830#post-4136227</guid>
				<title>Re: bazooper</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-97830/recent-forum-posts#post-4136227</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 31 Jan 2019 00:57:50 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Elogee FishTruck</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4037075</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well, this is a bit of a necropost, but it is that time of year again, and I'm gonna satisfy this guy's demand once and for all.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Show&nbsp;Epic&nbsp;Love&nbsp;Poem</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Hide&nbsp;Epic&nbsp;Love&nbsp;Poem</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Dead Memes and Series One Dreams</span></p> <p>I have but one request for you<br /> this date of Valentine.<br /> Please let me know my dreams are true<br /> And that you will be mine.<br /> The finest pill I have given<br /> To you, my love, so fine<br /> For it has been so edited<br /> By the Clockworks divine.<br /> Please gaze upon this pretty sheam,<br /> Perfection this does shine.<br /> The richness of your soul does gleam<br /> As if it was aged wine.<br /> If I must be a cultured lad,<br /> Unlike a putrid swine,<br /> Your Chungus posts make me so glad.<br /> Please be my Valentine.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
